This new initiative has only further strengthened the country’s fragmentation.
From the point of view of the opposition, the president persists in his "autocratic delirium", continues to "abuse his word" and "slows the law".
However, his supporters assure that it is a means to reverse the constitutional and political crisis as quickly as possible and speed up the transition process.
